==Hindi==

===Expression===
'''दूर के ढोल सुहावने''' (dūr ke dhol suhāvne)

# [[the grass is always greener on the other side]]

===Usage===
The full phrase requires a verb and may be something like:
*दूर के ढोल सुहावने होते हैं (dūr ke dhol suhāvne hote hai.n) lit. distant drums pleasant/pleasing are
*दूर के ढोल सुहावने लगते हैं (dūr ke dhol suhāvne lagte hai.n) lit. distant drums pleasant seem/feel

